<text top="679" left="90" width="69" height="19" font="6"><b>Agenda</b></text>
<text top="721" left="122" width="395" height="14" font="1">The situation concerning the Democratic Republic of the Congo</text>
<text top="757" left="153" width="675" height="14" font="1">Report of the Secretary-General on the United Nations Preliminary Deployment in the Democratic Republic of</text>
